        <item>
            <title>Version 1.3</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 22:45:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>1.3</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:releaseNotesLink>https://github.com/Xtron6/-cardrunner-releases/releases/tag/v1.3</sparkle:releaseNotesLink>
            <description><![CDATA[Custom Folder destination mode — pick any folder on your Mac (NAS, RAID, internal drive) instead of only connected SSDs. Date folders are still auto-created inside. | Light mode contrast overhaul — deeper blue and purple on all UI elements, ring, pills, and queue rows. | Smooth scrolling — all panels now use AppKit-backed momentum scrolling with elastic bounce. | Speed graph appears instantly when a transfer starts instead of after 10–15 seconds. | History panel now resets at the same broadcast-day cutoff as session stats instead of a fixed 24 hours. | Destination tabs (SSD / Custom Folder) now have a sliding pill animation, hover states, and full-area click targets. | Stale custom dest path detected on launch — orange warning shown if the chosen folder is missing or unmounted. | Several edge-case fixes: canIngest no longer does sync filesystem I/O on every render, SmoothScrollView now correctly tracks content height changes, card-detection scan excludes the custom destination volume.]]></description>
